level_lore = "Once, watchmen guarded the fields with nothing more than patience and trust. Now, silent figures roam beside mechanical eyes that never tire, watching over the land as it slowly bends to a new order. They call it progress, yet with every passing day, the distance between people and the earth quietly grows."
